title: Reserved/Gated Parking * USB Plug Outlets * Newer 2+2 Loft in Glendale
posting_body: ['Unit Availability: October 5, 2022', 'Introducing the L Lofts Living Experience!', "Enjoy a newly built community with luxury amenities in a walkable/bike friendly neighborhood adjacent to Glendale's best restaurants, shopping and entertainment.", "L Lofts has 42 luxe units from studio's to dual level lofts in a complex that includes a plush garden courtyard with barbecue, a state-of- the-art gym, 5 theaters and a restaurant.", '201-215 North Maryland Avenue', 'Glendale, CA', 'show contact info', 'AMENITIES:', '- Under Cabinet Strip Lights', '- Gated and Private Storage for Residents', '- UFC Sponsored Gym', '- Natural Water Feature', '- Electric Vehicle Charging Station', '- Built-in USB Outlets', '- Recessed LED Lights', '- High-end Front Loading Washer & Dryer', '- Large Walk-in Closets', '- Nest Learning Thermostat', "- Chef's Island in Select Units", '- Modern Stainless Steel Finish Appliances', '- Complimentary Wi-Fi Throughout Building', '- Ground Floor Dining and Entertainment', '- Balcony With Great Views in Select Units', '- Signature Luxury Interior Finishes', '- 24-hour On-site Manager and Maintenance Personnel', '- Community Fire Place With Benches', '- Close Distance to All Major Restaurants and Shops', '- Bike Storage', '- Laemmle Theater and Panda Inn Restaurant Commercial Space On Premise', '- Controlled Access Building Entry', '- Reserved and Gated Garage Parking', '- Two Community Courtyards With Furniture and Barbeque Grills', 'Price & availability are subject to change.', 'Sq footage may not be exact.', 'Pictures may not be of exact Unit.']
